{
  "info": {
    "name": "Mini Mercado Livre — API Gateway",
    "_postman_id": "f6a7b8c9-d0e1-2345-f012-34567890abcd",
    "description": "Ponto de entrada único do Mini Mercado Livre.\nBase URL: {{base_url}} (default: http://localhost:8079)\n\nTodos os microsserviços são acessados via este gateway.\nO JWT é validado aqui antes de ser roteado ao downstream.\n\nConvenção de paths:\n  /api/v1/products/**    → catalog-service   :8081\n  /api/v1/orders/**     → order-service     :8082\n  /api/v1/payments/**   → payment-service   :8083\n  /api/v1/inventory/**  → inventory-service :8084\n  /api/v1/reservations/** → inventory-service :8084\n  /api/v1/shippings/**  → shipping-service  :8085\n  /api/v1/notifications/** → notification-service :8086\n\nO script de pré-requisição da coleção obtém o token do Keycloak\nautomaticamente. Configure as variáveis keycloak_user e keycloak_pass.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "// Auto-obtém token do Keycloak (user1 por padrão)",
          "const tokenUrl = 'http://localhost:8080/realms/mini-mercado-livre/protocol/openid-connect/token';",
          "const username = pm.collectionVariables.get('keycloak_user') || 'user1';",
          "const password = pm.collectionVariables.get('keycloak_pass') || 'user1pass';",
          "const clientId = 'mini-ml-frontend';",
          "",
          "const expiresAt = pm.collectionVariables.get('token_expires_at');",
          "if (!expiresAt || Date.now() >= parseInt(expiresAt)) {",
          "    pm.sendRequest({",
          "        url: tokenUrl,",
          "        method: 'POST',",
          "        header: { 'Content-Type': 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded' },",
          "        body: {",
          "            mode: 'urlencoded',",
          "            urlencoded: [",
          "                { key: 'grant_type', value: 'password' },",
          "                { key: 'client_id', value: clientId },",
          "                { key: 'username', value: username },",
          "                { key: 'password', value: password }",
          "            ]",
          "        }",
          "    }, (err, res) => {",
          "        if (err) { console.error('Erro ao obter token:', err); return; }",
          "        const body = res.json();",
          "        pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', body.access_token);",
          "        pm.collectionVariables.set('token_expires_at', Date.now() + (body.expires_in - 30) * 1000);",
          "        console.log('Token renovado para usuário:', username);",
          "    });",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url",           "value": "http://localhost:8079" },
    { "key": "access_token",       "value": "" },
    { "key": "admin_token",        "value": "", "description": "Token admin1/admin1pass (ROLE_ADMIN)" },
    { "key": "token_expires_at",   "value": "0" },
    { "key": "keycloak_user",      "value": "user1",     "description": "Usuário para auto-login" },
    { "key": "keycloak_pass",      "value": "user1pass", "description": "Senha para auto-login" },
    { "key": "ultimo_pedido_id",   "value": "" },
